[quote=“The Reaper X, post:36, topic:5119”]It’s just another excuse for impersonal comunication. i wish myspace didn’t exist only because it is another impersonal way of chatting. although so is this forum =\ idk, either way i don’t really care too much about stuff like that. It’s only good for talking about stuff important in real life, like invitations, scheduals.

The thing i hate the most about myspace is how serious people take your “Top Friends”. They’re pictures, they don’t have to be in a certain order. and besides, if i did put someone in order from my closest friends to the least, screw off it’s the truth. if you wanna be higher on my effing myspace then maybe you should talk to me more? Am i right? the whole thing is stupid, causes arguments for nothing…[/quote]

You will never understand.
